Modifications.Value: Causes a target enemy unit to be bound to the ground so that it cannot move for <Aens,Dur2> seconds. Air units that are ensnared can be attacked as though they were land units.

Causes enemy air units in a target area to be bound to the ground with a 50% chance per unit for <A0F3,Dur1> seconds. Air units that are successfully ensnared can be attacked as though they were land units.
